import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.boxplot(data['Penicillin'])
    plt.xticks([1], ['Penicillin'])
    plt.title("What is the distribution of Penicillin across all bacteria?")
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.boxplot(data['Streptomycin'])
    plt.title("What is the distribution of Streptomycin across all bacteria?")
    plt.xlabel("Streptomycin")
    plt.ylabel("Values")
    plt.xticks([1], ['Streptomycin'])
    plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.scatter(data['Penicillin'], data['Streptomycin'])
    plt.xlabel('Penicillin')
    plt.ylabel('Streptomycin')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.title("What is the relationship between Penicillin and Streptomycin?", wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    gram_positive_data = data[data['Gram_Staining'] == 'positive']
    plt.hist(gram_positive_data['Neomycin'])
    plt.xlabel('Neomycin')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of Neomycin for Gram-positive bacteria?')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
